INSERT INTO `user_thanks_comments` VALUES (21,2,2,'Kailash Suresh','Thank you, Madhu for all the fun times prior to and during Hult!','2017-08-18 07:43:47','2017-08-18 07:43:47'),(22,2,22,'Kailash Suresh','Always fun playing with you! And thank you for lunch :)','2017-08-19 22:25:51','2017-08-19 22:25:51'),(23,16,23,'Rodica','Glad you liked it!','2017-08-20 17:57:13','2017-08-20 17:57:13'),(24,17,25,'Sumana Samuk','Awww.. thank you too Madhu. For being the positive energy during my journey at HULT. Wishing you all the very best in everything you do. Keep those beliefs strong, don\'t let anyone tell you otherwise.','2017-08-21 00:44:16','2017-08-21 00:44:16'),(25,1,25,'Madhu Prabhakara','Thanks a lot Som, those are powerful words.','2017-08-21 00:57:02','2017-08-21 00:57:02'),(29,1,34,'Madhu Prabhakara','Rosey is an eternally warm person, never makes you feel left out!','2017-08-24 23:07:10','2017-08-24 23:07:10'),(30,19,36,'Sidharth Vijayan','You are pure positivity and a pure soul Madhu. No one can take that away from you. This is a brilliant platform for gratitude, something that is lacking in the world. Let\'s bring out the best in people...','2017-08-25 00:29:49','2017-08-25 00:29:49'),(31,1,38,'Madhu Prabhakara','I second that, your Quality of being of help to people is something that is rarely seen in people. Don\'t ever change.','2017-08-25 20:01:32','2017-08-25 20:01:32'),(32,33,34,'Rosey Singh','Thanks Ahmad.   Our love went both ways.  You supported me just as much and when I needed it the most.  Thank you for being so wonderful!','2017-08-27 18:55:50','2017-08-27 18:55:50'),(33,33,2,'Rosey Singh','Thank you Madhu for your joyful nature and fun spirit.  Your laugh was definitely contagious. I\'m happy to have met a person like you!   Wish you and your family all the love life has to offer.','2017-08-27 18:57:14','2017-08-27 18:57:14'),(34,34,21,'Sinthia Rojas','Great words Madhu! I enjoyed working with you guys! It was amazing!','2017-08-27 19:44:47','2017-08-27 19:44:47'),(35,2,33,'Kailash Suresh','Thanks for being there ! Following the ebb and sound of music always !','2017-08-27 22:02:17','2017-08-27 22:02:17'),(36,1,33,'Madhu Prabhakara','Kailash is a kick ass musician and I have had the privilege  of watching him live in couple of his shows and it was amazing!','2017-08-28 00:20:18','2017-08-28 00:20:18'),(37,36,15,'Ray DeRenzo','Madhu, glad to be of help. You are a true serial entrepreneur, able to work on two inspired concepts like Walleee and Thankingli  at the same time. Best of luck and happy to offer my support.','2017-08-28 19:25:41','2017-08-28 19:25:41'),(38,2,40,'Kailash Suresh','Well, The first time we met was catching pokemon before the game was officially released in India :) Its been so nice meeting you, sharing the apartment together and many memories. To many more happier years of annoying each other :D','2017-08-30 07:10:40','2017-08-30 07:10:40'),(39,17,41,'Sumana Samuk','Hahahaha.. That is the sweetest thing ever. I just want to thank you for being you! Keep that going. And wait, I want the long one. Email me?You know am a sucker for verbiage. Right? ?\r\n\r\nThank you for not picking fluffy. Did you buy the snake from Snape\'s class? ?','2017-08-30 13:46:10','2017-08-30 13:46:10'),(40,39,10,'Reem Fatayri','These are such beautiful words! It was indeed one of the best teams ever. I am very happy to have worked with you Madhu. You are an inspiration and you spread positive vibes all around you.','2017-08-30 20:00:16','2017-08-30 20:00:16'),(41,1,41,'Madhu Prabhakara','Sorry Shri, Will make sure the platform doesn\'t come in the way of people expressing their emotions. Have made necessary changes.','2017-08-31 01:02:46','2017-08-31 01:02:46'),(42,17,41,'Sumana Samuk','? Madhu! You are not supposed to read these private messages ??','2017-08-31 02:05:18','2017-08-31 02:05:18'),(43,1,41,'Madhu Prabhakara','Shri has thanked you for making a difference in his life, let the world know what you are made of!','2017-08-31 03:55:50','2017-08-31 03:55:50'),(44,17,41,'Sumana Samuk','?? can I add this on my Resume? This should work atleast','2017-08-31 05:32:02','2017-08-31 05:32:02'),(45,1,41,'Madhu Prabhakara','Lol, May be someday people will look at this as well.','2017-08-31 06:00:30','2017-08-31 06:00:30'),(46,1,43,'Madhu Prabhakara','Goodness, thanks a lot Vijay. Not sure if I deserve such warmth but I am sure our friendship is something that I am going to treasure for life.','2017-09-02 05:18:01','2017-09-02 05:18:01'),(47,38,43,'VIJAY','You certainly do Madhukar!  ;-)','2017-09-03 04:09:36','2017-09-03 04:09:36'),(48,32,37,'harshith','I am sure you would agree the feeling is quite mutual Madhukar. I am extremely happy to have met you, Vijay and Satheesh at a very precise phase of our life, did not have as many things to worry then. I don\'t think I\'ll ever get to witness the same chemistry with anyone again.','2017-09-06 22:16:54','2017-09-06 22:16:54'),(49,32,37,'harshith','If I have to answer someone \"who is the most hard-working, simple or a person extremely positive\", your name would top my list any day. I am sure your hard work will take you far and the days to come will get you busier but some day I hope we can finish our incomplete Goa trip. :-)','2017-09-06 22:17:35','2017-09-06 22:17:35'),(50,1,37,'Madhu Prabhakara','Thanks a lot Harshith you guys are way too warm, and I am inspired by all that I have experienced with you guys. And I started this mission just so people can express gratitude for all the little things that add up to make their life what it is today.','2017-09-06 23:03:32','2017-09-06 23:03:32'),(51,2,45,'Kailash Suresh','This is such a sweet message! Thanks for sharing.','2017-09-09 19:49:58','2017-09-09 19:49:58'),(52,42,44,'Brett Noyes','Thanks so much for the kind words.  I wish you both the best of luck in your careers.','2017-09-19 16:36:22','2017-09-19 16:36:22'),(53,43,43,'Janani','Dear Maddy buddy,\r\n\r\nYayyyyy Congratulations on the launch of thankingli :)\r\nIts a very novel thought and concept ..I am very happy for you and proud of you :)\r\n\r\nAll the very super best and my best wishes will always be with you for anything and everything...!!! Yayyy keep rocking :)\r\n\r\nCheers and smiles,\r\n~Jan','2017-09-20 14:58:35','2017-09-20 14:58:35'),(55,1,3,'Madhu Prabhakara','So you just tested if the system works. Thank God it does LOL :-)','2017-09-20 16:16:10','2017-09-20 16:16:10'),(56,44,29,'Maïté Chennangattu','Sid, having you in my life is a blessing. You are one of the few people in my life that I can call \"a friend\".','2017-09-21 22:46:05','2017-09-21 22:46:05'),(57,2,55,'Kailash Suresh','I am going to check this place out! Thanks!','2017-10-03 18:52:01','2017-10-03 18:52:01'),(58,49,52,'Tazza D’Amore Cafe','Hi Sidharth - THANK YOU for taking the time to write such nice things about our Barista. We absolutely appreciate it! \r\n\r\nWe’ve shared your message with our team, and it’s people like you that motivate us to get up early and work tirelessly to make sure our customers leave happy. \r\n\r\nThank you again, \r\n\r\nMarkus Merlino \r\nOwner \r\nTazza D’Amore Cafe \r\n@ 4th/King Caltrain','2017-10-03 18:52:41','2017-10-03 18:52:41'),(59,1,52,'Madhu Prabhakara','I am going to check this place out soon!','2017-10-03 19:30:34','2017-10-03 19:30:34'),(60,50,57,'Lance Landgren','Madhu, \r\nYou just made my night, week.... month with this comment. :) \r\nI\'m so glad we were able to take care of you and connect you with that amazing Chicken Under a Brick. \r\nAsk for me any time you\'re in. :)  I look forward to seeing you two our again soon. \r\nThank you, \r\nLance Landgren','2017-10-07 04:23:04','2017-10-07 04:23:04');
